('My Hero MAN WITH A MISSION', 0)_{'sear.description:
Opening for Log Horizon
Counteraction rising, Yeh we are ready for the, punch, line!
There's no use with all your gimmicks, so CHECK THIS OUT

Cool bomb stuff and lots of movement, Expert+ is big swings and very stamina
draining. It is quite a decent map set so give it a shot!

Enjoy!
